  "detailed_description": "Embark on this unique experience as you take control of your character's hands using two mouse controllers. One mouse guides the left hand, while the other directs the other, offering a unique and engaging gameplay mechanic that challenges your coordination skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/350aa3c841ab4047425b6505553d3b9b.poster.avif?t=1712950691\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/350aa3c841ab4047425b6505553d3b9b.webm?t=1712950691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/350aa3c841ab4047425b6505553d3b9b.mp4?t=1712950691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Engage with a diverse range of levers and buttons to masterfully command intricate machinery within the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/15f84b8aab192ded386dda194f5f94f6.poster.avif?t=1712950691\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/15f84b8aab192ded386dda194f5f94f6.webm?t=1712950691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/15f84b8aab192ded386dda194f5f94f6.mp4?t=1712950691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore multiple game modes, each presenting distinctive mechanics and challenges that will keep you hooked and entertained.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/115a7e65e3b0c25e4d01b9e3203f0f9c.poster.avif?t=1712950691\" width=612 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/115a7e65e3b0c25e4d01b9e3203f0f9c.webm?t=1712950691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2866700/extras/115a7e65e3b0c25e4d01b9e3203f0f9c.mp4?t=1712950691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Future Content</h2>Look forward to a continuous stream of free exhilarating content updates. The possibilities are boundless, with upcoming game modes such as piloting planes, navigating construction vehicles in chaotic scenarios, underwater adventures with submarines, high-speed kart races, and epic space battles.",
